name: Jarvis
description: Jarvis is an AI-centric memecoin project that aims to integrate artificial intelligence within the crypto space. Built on the Solana blockchain through pump.fun, Jarvis represents a character from pop culture known for its intelligence and assistance, embodying a digital assistant that resonates with meme culture. The project uses a meme generator to create the viral images of the Jarvis trend to be shared amongst friends. An AI Agent, connected to an X account, is learning to respond to community engagement in real time.
